keyFacts: The flight was scheduled to depart from West Palm Beach, Florida, at 4:00 PM and arrive in New York at 6:16 PM.
The aircraft used for the flight was a B-727 with a titanium color.
The flight crew included Captain David Rodgers, Co-Captain Larry Visoski, and Engineer Larry Morrison.
